{"tid":498330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回收膠樽] 噉我每次洗樽搣招紙嚟做咩?","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:06:17.000Z","uid":37125,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5110aab6b5e9fd6a23afbf46f38117c2361f762d","tid":498330,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513157241_4f6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513157241_4f6c.jpg&h=c0475d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府指2015年飲品膠樽的回收率只有7.6%，即9成多膠樽被運往堆填區棄置。環保團體綠色地球調查發現，84%回收公司已拒絕回收膠樽，本港公私營屋苑的回收系統瀕臨崩潰，促當局擴大中央回收廢膠運輸系統至公屋、居屋，覆蓋全港45%人口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57575395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57575395&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNstU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cacef296\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57575395&h=6cb44c87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57575395</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 圖中又有幾多個膠樽係搣咗招紙㗎呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0d0e883f3e2ceee99a8668eb698938f747f138","tid":498330,"uid":33681,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"搣招紙 拆個蓋同環 洗乾淨原來無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我仲係街飲完野做齊先放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f898397bb54342bcbedd7650b7485ec5cededc1","tid":498330,"uid":50032,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:35:10.000Z","msg":"on9 先會拎去回出收<br />\n<br />\n利申: 發夢見過d 呀姐拎回收d 樽直上堆填車"},{"pid":"406b08b1160a268fdd9758adc8cb41ff2abc75e8","tid":498330,"uid":37666,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"香港搞環保真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c1ab6121c3c230421a1b8331728edb079eaa44","tid":498330,"uid":130105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港搞環保真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錢賺；基本上，外國係紙同金屬環保有錢賺，其他要保貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5174e19f3a4aa4ca29ddc0c8f3faed13fb0d93ce","tid":498330,"uid":37125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搣招紙 拆個蓋同環 洗乾淨原來無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我仲係街飲完野做齊先放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗香港永遠都冇可能做到日本嗰個程度."},{"pid":"54dc69443d7c89714d795d513f966a330ccb0cf1","tid":498330,"uid":130105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港搞環保真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錢賺；基本上，外國係紙同金屬環保有錢賺，其他要保貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再講多句，其實蝗國都進口大量回收膠樽做返原材料，應該同廢紙回收一樣，又係香港自已攪衰咗唔知乜野，變咗冇得玩。<br />\n我話保貼，唔係話正苦要派錢攪，而係正苦要當佢唔係商業市場咁計。"},{"pid":"1f40c33f269b5e9bef60f5463db7cd1f1e77f9f4","tid":498330,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港搞環保真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錢賺；基本上，外國係紙同金屬環保有錢賺，其他要保貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地國家有工業, 回收之後可以整成原材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12658a48ef7346afd359b0854e9af55a5f552099","tid":498330,"uid":130105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搣招紙 拆個蓋同環 洗乾淨原來無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我仲係街飲完野做齊先放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗香港永遠都冇可能做到日本嗰個程度.</blockquote><br />\n加拿大都唔洗搣招紙、拆個蓋同環，香港攪乜，環保公司有機器攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08796c928df1ee0ced916e786c2edda079ff389f","tid":498330,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d68355d5d32b0c965f5a1fc66142833b81d6411","tid":498330,"uid":37666,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T21:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港搞環保真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錢賺；基本上，外國係紙同金屬環保有錢賺，其他要保貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁香港本身有錢呀麻<br />\n搞環保回饋社會都應該啦<br />\n捐錢比北京又識搞環保又唔識<br />\n香港班狗官正仆街黎"},{"pid":"ce454a62aac5e3c41b2edceca6068fca4b615be6","tid":498330,"uid":72581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T21:56:57.000Z","msg":"應該收膠樽稅強制回收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f61807881520a0961ddc28d88052c3ba1289be0","tid":498330,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搣招紙 拆個蓋同環 洗乾淨原來無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我仲係街飲完野做齊先放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗香港永遠都冇可能做到日本嗰個程度.</blockquote><br />\n加拿大都唔洗搣招紙、拆個蓋同環，香港攪乜，環保公司有機器攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明係日本奴性<br />\n稅就俾咗<br />\n反而要麻煩自己<br />\n外國人仲要舐日舐到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"f7c0719bea3935e8a8b68ce8e3e1143a4d6501a6","tid":498330,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:07:27.000Z","msg":"點解大家唔屌回收公司？"},{"pid":"6d572dcc48b04f5e3d30689cd484d5ed26cbb059","tid":498330,"uid":51720,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:40:48.000Z","msg":"日本、台灣嘅回收膠樽，還原成再生膠粒後，<br />\n有D甚至製成人造纖維，成為體育服裝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94477de370c34e4bb1779996d85d264d750780a4","tid":498330,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔明政府點解唔包底"},{"pid":"6ccd42e2951378b35e90a98bdbee97cdb70042a8","tid":498330,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解大家唔屌回收公司？</blockquote><br />\n屌佢地唔識賺錢？"},{"pid":"323f0d72a5956ed1ee87260a625683c7a26d815d","tid":498330,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明政府點解唔包底</blockquote><br />\n會俾人屌利益輸送"},{"pid":"124dce8f2ffde80978790f5e1a8f6ece63419773","tid":498330,"uid":55732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:51:00.000Z","msg":"原來揼落回收箱都係自我感覺良好咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港真係冇撚得救"},{"pid":"2abdc4396e58ecfea98bbff8de809390b49a6d69","tid":498330,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:52:05.000Z","msg":"用多d水囉<br />\n<br />\n香港根本搞唔到環保，地貴，但做回收就係要地，<br />\n同埋回收完d物料要有出路先得"},{"pid":"d98048d70f4f6414a87f0225a6f3dc316192d382","tid":498330,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔明政府點解唔包底</blockquote><br />\n會俾人屌利益輸送</blockquote><br />\n科學園就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實政府係唔識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd1e63e2cff9cb5b7410a8fe8c10ab27b8b9576","tid":498330,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用多d水囉<br />\n<br />\n香港根本搞唔到環保，地貴，但做回收就係要地，<br />\n同埋回收完d物料要有出路先得</blockquote><br />\n出路一定有，蝗國都運美國既回收膠樽返去做原材料，香港人自已攪衰曬冇得講<br />\n<br />\n地點會係問題"},{"pid":"991faacd33719c86b2a6395168ff95b422cd7438","tid":498330,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來揼落回收箱都係自我感覺良好咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港真係冇撚得救</blockquote><br />\n仲等我成日都拎住個樽on99咁行到有回收箱為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後都係丟落垃圾桶算撚數"},{"pid":"7e34ed464533ad5d182e226c2f1970902ef544f6","tid":498330,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環保撚除咗賣膠袋數銀紙識春咩"},{"pid":"ba5a71fa3e7dba9a3ae8e70f8a13210d6042add4","tid":498330,"uid":9577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"九月份的舊聞有提到政府考慮搞中央回收<br />\n只係唔知由研究到落實要幾耐時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>環保署研由政府收集廢膠樽</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170905/20143244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170905%2F20143244&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNstU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=27019304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170905%2F20143244&h=6a34e969\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170905/20143244</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】環保署8月曾與內地環保部門開會，商討國內收緊回收物料進口標準。該署副署長郭黃穎琦承認新標準對廢紙及廢塑料影響較大，署方會研究多項措施，包括破天荒考慮由政府中央收集廢膠樽，統一收集各社區中心或其他源頭的廢膠樽，再運往合資格的回收商處理。明年起擴大資助各區18個回收中心，按需要接收私人屋苑及住宅廢膠樽。<br />\n研究引入生產者責任計劃<br />\n當局並研究把盛載飲料和個人護理產品的塑膠容器，引入生產者責任計劃。在處理廢紙回收方面，環保署和海事處已提供16個專供廢紙回收商競投使用的公眾貨物裝卸區停泊位，供回收商處理並裝運廢紙出口。<br />\n對於有回收商現已無法出口回收物料至內地，郭黃穎琦無正面回應可如何解決。環保署助理署長黃漢明昨承認，暫時沒有各類廢紙比例數據，他認為大部份廢紙經分揀後均可出口，不會棄置在堆填區。<br />\n綠惜地球環境倡議總監朱漢強指，若政府依靠18個回收中心，無法收集足夠塑膠，提供予本地循環再造。他認為如果有足夠誘因，本港逾400個街邊回收店可組成回收網絡，供應廢塑膠予循環再造商，開動分揀機和拉粒機，真正做到本地循環再造。他指本港擁有循環再造膠粒的廠房，大多向國外購買廢塑膠，而非向回收舖購買塑膠。<br />\n■記者潘柏林"}]}